ok]]''\n* [[Josh Gad]], [[Luke Evans]] & [[Alan Menken]] perform ''[[Gaston (song)|Gaston]]'' from ''[[Beauty and the Beast (1991 film)|Beauty and the Beast]]''\n* [[Donny Osmond]] (& his grandkids) sing ''[[I'll Make a Man Out of You]]'' ''[[Mulan (1998 film)|Mulan]]''\n* [[Tracee Ellis Ross]] introduces [[Christina Aguilera]] singing ''[[Can You Feel The Love Tonight]]'' from ''[[The Lion King]]''\n* [[Jordan Fisher]] sings ''[[Under the Sea]]'' from ''[[The Little Mermaid (1989 film)|The Little Mermaid]]''\n* [[Tori Kelly]] sings ''[[Colors Of The Wind]]'' from ''[[Pocahontas (1995 film)|Pocahontas]]''\n* [[John Stamos]], [[Caitlin McHugh]] & their son Billy perform ''[[It's a Small World (After All)]]''\n* [[Thomas Rhett]] sings ''[[Do You Want to Build a Snowman?]]'' from ''[[Frozen (2013 film)|Frozen]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/country/thomas-rhett-joined-by-daughters-disney-singalong-special/|title=Thomas Rhett and His Daughters Perform Song from Frozen for Disney Singalong Special|website=PEOPLE.com}}</ref>\n* [[Zac Efron]] introduces [[Kenny Ortega]] & ''[[High School Musical]]'' cast members [[Vanessa Hudgens]], [[Ashley Tisdale]], [[Monique Coleman]], [[Lucas Grabeel]], [[Corbin Bleu]] & [[Kaycee Stroh]] as they perform ''We're All In This Together'' along with [[Sofia Carson]], [[Dove Cameron]], [[Sarah Jeffery]] & [[Booboo Stewart]] from ''[[Descendants 3]]'' & [[Milo Manheim]] from ''[[Zombies (2018 film)|Zombies]]'' .<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a32174424/why-zac-efron-not-singing-high-school-musical-reunion-disney-singalong/|title=Why Zac Efron Isn't Singing With the 'High School Musical' Cast in the Disney Family Singalong|first=Alyssa|last=Bailey|date=April 16, 2020|website=ELLE}}</ref>\n* [[Michael Buble]] & [[Demi Lovato]] sing ''[[A Dream Is a Wish Your Heart Makes]]'' from ''[[Cinderella (1950 film)|Cinderella]]''\n* [[Elizabeth Olsen]]\n* [[Sebastian Stan]]\n* [[Jeff Goldblum]]\n* [[Paul Bettany]]\