ane MacDonaghs GAA|Kilruane MacDonaghs]] 2-11, 0-05 (R)\n|-\n| 1974\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 3-06\n| [[Silvermines GAA|Silvermines]] 1-10\n|-\n| 1973\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 3-14\n| [[Kilruane MacDonaghs GAA|Kilruane MacDonaghs]] 3-08\n|-\n| 1972\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 5-08\n| [[Borris-Ileigh GAA|Borris-Ileigh]] 3-06\n|-\n| 1971\n| [[Moyne-Templetouhy GAA|Moyne-Templetuohy]] 2-08\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 0-06\n|-\n| 1970\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 3-11\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 2-12\n|-\n| 1969\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 4-13\n| [[Carrick Davins GAA|Carrick Davins]] 0-05\n|-\n| 1968\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 2-13\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 3-04\n|-\n| 1967\n| [[Carrick Davins GAA|Carrick Davins]] 2-10\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 2-07\n|-\n| 1966\n| [[Carrick Davins GAA|Carrick Davins]] 2-12\n| [[Lorrha-Dorrha GAA|Lorrha]] 1-02\n|-\n| 1965\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 2-07, 3-11 (R)\n| [[Carrick Davins GAA|Carrick Davins]] 3-04, 2-07 (R)\n|-\n| 1964\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 5-14\n| [[Holycross-Ballycahill GAA|Holycross-Ballycahill]] 1-04\n|-\n| 1963\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 4-10\n| [[Roscrea GAA|Roscrea]] 2-10\n|-\n| 1962\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 1-07\n| [[Moycarkey-Borris GAA|Moycarkey-Borris]] 1-06\n|- \n| 1961\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 3-04\n| [[Toomevara GAA|Toomevara]] 0-09\n|-\n| 1960\n| [[Toomevara GAA|Toomevara]] 3-15\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 2-08\n|-\n| 1959\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 3-12\n| [[Kilruane MacDonaghs GAA|Kilruane MacDonaghs]] 2-06\n|-\n| 1958\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 4-11\n| [[Toomevara GAA|Toomevara]] 3-03\n|-\n| 1957\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 4-15\n| Na Piarsaigh 4-04\n|-\n| 1956\n| [[Thurles Sarsfields GAA|Thurles Sarsfields]] 3-08\n| [[Lorrha-Dorrha GAA|Lorrha